# Enforce absolute Line Feed (LF) normalization across all text files in the repository index to guarantee deterministic cryptographic hashing and zero-noise diffs across mixed-OS contributor environments.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicitly mark binary assets to prevent Git from attempting text-based diffs or line ending conversions, which corrupts the payload.
*.ico binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.dll binary
*.exe binary
